4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer," which is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field. The course prepares students for a career as a data scientist and provides training in building machine learning models. The program is 16 weeks long and offers classes three times a week. The class size is limited to 12 people.

The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, as well as supervised and unsupervised learning models. Practical exercises and real-life case studies are included to prepare students for challenges they may face in their careers.

Instructors for the course include professionals with extensive experience in the field, such as Sayyed Nezhadi, who holds a PhD in Artificial Intelligence. Francesco Pugliese, a Computer Scientist and PhD in Robotics & Artificial Intelligence, also teaches the course. Manuel Mena, a Senior Data Scientist with experience in Machine Learning and Business Intelligence, is another instructor.

Upon completion of the course, students receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is required to enroll, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. Live classes are taught in the language of the campus.

For more information about the course, you can visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop